snippet.title: SNES Longplay - Super Mario World
snippet.description:
100% no-commentary playthrough -- all level exits and Dragon Coins are shown. This was recorded on the snes9x emulator. I did die more than a few times - I edited out the deaths afterwards, so none of them appear in the video. I also did a bit of editing towards the end of the video, in the final level. Normally the player just picks two rooms and can't access the other six, but for completion's sake I decided to show all of them.

You might notice that I crouch a lot, seemingly at random. That's just my USB controller being weird.

You are free to use this footage in your own video if you wish, so long as this video and channel are credited in your video/description.
